author: gstein
msg: We require SQLite 3.6.18 at configure time, so let's also code that into
the module and strip out code for older version.
(...): several cosmetic changes: whitespace, comment style, etc
(): add #error for old versions of SQLite
(init_sqlite): remove #if statements since we have already verified a
(internal_open): remove #if check for recent version, and remove a big
block of code for now-obsolete older versions of SQLite.
(svn_sqlite__with_lock): remove #if checks that are no longer needed
(svn_sqlite__hotcopy): remove an #if check, and a block of code that
only applies to now-obsolete older SQLite.
